About Me

I’m a rising senior at UT Austin with a passion for venture capital, technology investing, data science, and product. I have internship experience on the M&A deal team at the TMT holding company Stagwell (Summer 2025) and in data science and product at the e-commerce tech startup Arcade.ai (Summer 2024). Back on campus, I help run the VC club Texas Venture Group.
